---
const title = "Stakater | Red Hat Partner Decks";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #FF5623;
      --dark:    #1A0D32;
      --gray:    #5a5668;
      --light:   #F5F5F5;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background: white;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .header {
      padding: 40px 60px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 60px 60px 70px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 72px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--gray);
      max-width: 520px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .decks-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 60px 100px;
    }

    .deck-card {
      background: var(--light);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 48px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
      display: block;
      position: relative;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .deck-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(26,13,50,0.12);
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .deck-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .deck-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .deck-desc {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--gray);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .deck-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .deck-cta {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .deck-slides {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .exec-card {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: white;
    }

    .exec-card .deck-label  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
    .exec-card .deck-title  { color: white; }
    .exec-card .deck-desc   { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
    .exec-card .deck-cta    { color: #FF5623; }
    .exec-card .deck-slides { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
    .exec-card:hover        { border-color: #FF5623; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">STAKATER</div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-label">Red Hat Partner Decks</div>
    <h1>Choose Your<br/>Audience.</h1>
    <p>Each deck is tailored to a specific Red Hat persona — same story, their language, their priorities.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="decks-grid">

    <a href="/ae" class="deck-card">
      <div class="deck-label">For →</div>
      <div class="deck-title">Enterprise Account Executive</div>
      <div class="deck-desc">ARR growth, account expansion, and protecting renewals in strategic named accounts. Speaks nodes, multi-year platforms, and renewal risk.</div>
      <div class="deck-footer">
        <span class="deck-cta">Open Deck →</span>
        <span class="deck-slides">9 slides</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/commercial" class="deck-card">
      <div class="deck-label">For →</div>
      <div class="deck-title">Commercial Sales Executive</div>
      <div class="deck-desc">Mid-market and SMB focus — portfolio pull-through, deal velocity, and upsell motion across ODF, ACM, ACS, and AMQ Streams.</div>
      <div class="deck-footer">
        <span class="deck-cta">Open Deck →</span>
        <span class="deck-slides">9 slides</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/partner" class="deck-card">
      <div class="deck-label">For →</div>
      <div class="deck-title">Partner Sales Executive</div>
      <div class="deck-desc">Co-sell motion, deal registration, and building a joint pipeline through lifecycle ownership. Speaks sourced, influenced, and registered.</div>
      <div class="deck-footer">
        <span class="deck-cta">Open Deck →</span>
        <span class="deck-slides">9 slides</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/exec" class="deck-card exec-card">
      <div class="deck-label">For →</div>
      <div class="deck-title">VP / Regional Director</div>
      <div class="deck-desc">Five slides. Numbers only. Strategic framing for leaders with limited time and high signal requirements.</div>
      <div class="deck-footer">
        <span class="deck-cta">Open Deck →</span>
        <span class="deck-slides">5 slides</span>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
